<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungaihnan ei tuom vel ie,
 Pi leh pu chana gitloh a dim;
 Van Lal cha lungsietna hin gitlohna cheng,
 A thisan in A sil thieng tai.

[V2]
 Kalvari tang chung achun,
 Ei Hukdampa Krista chun,
 Thisan in ei tan tai;
 &quot;Gitloh lakah hung pawt un&quot; A tii.

[V3]
 2. Ngai in, ei Hukdampa chun,
 Thawkna gen zawhsen loh chu thuokin;
 Tatna thisan chun melma cheng A nuoisieh tai,
 &quot;Tuhin hung pawt tau uo&quot; a tii.

[V4]
 3. Aw Lalpa nei sapna aw hi,
 Ka lunggil ahin a cham zing hi;
 Na lungngaihna aw gidawk chun &quot;ka dang a chak,
 Ka cha, ei tulh tau in&quot; Na tii.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Dang a Chak!</title>
<hymn_number>64</hymn_number>
</song>